{"tid":1689944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有傻鳩係將軍澳跌咗卡套","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:10:32.000Z","uid":69074,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"367ae6829d051f3ab1ca9fd31af38c38469a8ccf","tid":1689944,"uid":69074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"冇錯 個傻鳩就係我本人<br />\n<br />\n11月3號星期日中午時間約1230左右<br />\n因為趕巴士所以係唐明街跑去巴士站<br />\n懷疑奔跑途中跌咗八達通卡套<br />\n卡套內有八達通、學生證、會員證及情侶相片等物品<br />\n有冇將軍澳巴絲有見過個手工卡套<br />\n因為個卡套係女朋友送o既手工生日禮物<br />\n對我黎講極重要 希望拾取到o既巴絲可以聯絡我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjxLgzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjxLgzU.png&h=2649cef9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b227f86afa244ab67ae302050a2ed684b66771df","tid":1689944,"uid":69074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37c36ef840eb0b55de7e0b5185a9395d4e1fb2a","tid":1689944,"uid":69074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:37:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287adfce24b908ce60631294f4fd200e2cb8a772","tid":1689944,"uid":69074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d3defb78f653bc985200fdf0f27b66d7ba7bac","tid":1689944,"uid":102214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime